<P>
Friends of Kenneth Obney, who was slain just before Christmas by a gunman in a 
Santa Claus suit, raised nearly $1,200 for his widow, Mona, and their two 
teen-age children during a recent benefit at a Covina restaurant and bar. 
</P>
