<P>
FORMER TITAN NAMED SOFTBALL ASSISTANT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Connie Clark, a former All-American softball pitcher at Cal State Fullerton, 
has been named assistant softball coach at Florida State. Clark, a Garden Grove 
native, pitched for the Titans' 1986 national championship team. 
</P>
