VIDEO RENTALS 
</P>
<P>
A look at the fast-moving video rentals in three Orange County neighborhoods. 
</P>
<P>
THE VIDEO SHOPPE, 9592 Hamilton Ave., Huntington Beach. (714) 964-0969. 
</P>
<P>
