</P>
<P>
Great Balls of Fire (Orion) 
</P>
<P>
BLOCKBUSTER VIDEO, 1804 N. Placentia Ave., Placentia. (714) 524-9266. 
</P>
<P>
Do the Right Thing (MCA) 
</P>
<P>
License to Kill (CBS/Fox) 
</P>
<P>
Turner &amp; Hooch (Touchstone) 
</P>
<P>
Karate Kid Part III (RCA) 
</P>
<P>
The Adventures of Baron Munchhausen (RCA) 
</P>
<P>
VIDEOLAND, 712 El Camino Real, Tustin. (714) 838-1441. 
</P>
<P>
